To config factory default use: m_motor.getConfigurator().apply(new TalonFXConfiguration());

To config factory default use: m_motor.getConfigurator().apply(new TalonFXConfiguration());

For absolute sensor range create a cancoder configurator object and set this equal to any of the options in the AbsoluteSensorRangeValue enum: cancoder_config.MagnetSensor.AbsoluteSensorRange and setting factory default is the same as it is for the motor.
